  "texts": [
    "There are several possibilities for future improvements to our approach.",
    "Firstly, we augmented SuppKG with triples extracted from the SemMedDB database, indicating that all triples in our ADInt were obtained through literature-based discovery.",
    "In order to further enhance our knowledge graph, we can merge it with other comprehensive biomedical databases and biological networks, such as DrugBank and KEGG 65.",
    "This will enable us to expand the scope of our analysis and identify additional relevant interventions.",
    "Secondly, in addition to knowledge graph embedding and graph neural network models, other methods such as link prediction based on language models have also demonstrated promising results on LP tasks."
  ],
